A cyberpunk cityscape at night with glowing neon data streams flowing between towering skyscrapers, visualized as thin blue threads for text, medium orange cables for voice, and thick purple fiber optic bundles for video, all converging into a central holographic node pulsing with energy. Rain-slicked streets reflect the colorful bandwidth rivers above, while small drones zip along the data pathways. The scene emphasizes the contrast between delicate whisper-thin connections and massive data highways, creating a visual hierarchy of digital communication flowing through an urban matrix.
